snippet.title: Fidget Spinner (Ketchapp)
snippet.description:
Play iOS ➡ https://itunes.apple.com/app/finger-spinner/id1236104279?mt=8?at=11lGxL&ct=youtube-fingerspinner

Play Android ➡ https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ketchapp.fingerspinner

Most relaxing spinner is here!

You have 5 swipes to set the best spin you can. Wait for it to stop and sweep the sweet rewards! Upgrade the spinner, compete with your friends and beat the records!

Each spin brings you closer to unlocking a new spinner. Can you unlock them all?
